            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and cut your <strong>brown onion[s] </strong>into quarters, then separate the quarters so you end up with a pile of onion petals</p><p>Trim, then chop your <strong>green beans</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1678377030257-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
