            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli relish</strong>, <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>sriracha</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> in a small bowl with 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[175ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>sweet chilli sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
